column2: def factorial(n) if n == 0 1 else n * factorial(n - 1) end end
static bool IsPrime(int number) { if (number <= 1) return false; for (var i = 2; i < number; i++) if (number % i == 0) return false; return number > 1; }
function sumArray(array) { var sum = 0; for (var i = 0; i < array.length; i++) { sum += array[i]; } return sum; }
